{"tid":2048312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國人起義訴求：清算黑警","createTime":"2020-06-02T16:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T03:55:20.000Z","uid":231886,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30209635e95cf3824aa11b7411b5e388bb71eab8","tid":2048312,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/eric.cantona.77777/videos/10151224760279960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feric.cantona.77777%2Fvideos%2F10151224760279960&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2a72f800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/eric.cantona.77777/videos/10151224760279960</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">暴力，就是從你們身上學來的！</span><br />\n日常的暴力，特殊時刻的暴力，都源自制度的暴力。世途險惡，在中美大戰（新自由主義內戰）之時，要以吹棒法西斯政權來壓制法西斯政權，實在不敢苟同。與其向各地的壓迫者求助，我寧願跟其他抗爭者站在同一陣線。<br />\n2020年5月30日，美國民權行動者 Tamika Mallory 在抗議白人警員暴力殺人集會上，發表了精煉澎湃的演辭，字字珠璣、如雷貫耳。"},{"pid":"d7f955a47d6577a36a33d6e52db81f51c8f5a82c","tid":2048312,"uid":237487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港黑警呢？ </span></span></span>"},{"pid":"97363ad6b3215fbce939000eb6079c1081067201","tid":2048312,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7f955a47d6577a36a33d6e52db81f51c8f5a82c","tid":2048312,"uid":237487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港黑警呢？ </span></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求之一"},{"pid":"387e9266e06f3ee484ae1dbd3fe162c6040412e4","tid":2048312,"uid":271431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T17:01